text: Michelle Andres (born 26 May 1997 in Baden) is a Swiss road and track cyclist. From 2014 to 2020, she was a medallist at the Swiss national championships. She competed at the 2021 UCI Track Cycling World Championships. == References == == Other websites == * ICI Track Champions League Day One Michelle Andres of Switzerland changes her gear on day one Simon Parker (imago-images.com) Category:1997 births Category:Swiss cyclists Category:Sportspeople from Aargau Category:Living people
